{"tid":1224742,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［送終]政府話暫緩","createTime":"2019-06-15T04:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T02:06:14.000Z","uid":74595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f022180c4c746022c290c558becb3f3820013b","tid":1224742,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"一邊廂話暫緩 另一邊廂黑驚拉人<br />\n<br />\n彈弓手話唔開會 問起先話係未決定<br />\n<br />\n自發性執垃圾都可以屈藏鐵通磚頭<br />\n<br />\n搞鳩人物資站 散播謠言 分化市民<br />\n<br />\n如果今個星期日遊行人數少過上次 <br />\n<br />\n仲可以話市民轉撐送中 拎嚟打飛機<br />\n<br />\n星期一就名正言順繼續開會繼續推<br />\n<br />\n香港擁抱大灣區 上大陸唔使回鄉證<br />\n<br />\n連Hi都冇自由 到時我真係恭喜曬你<br />\n<br />\n總之徹回 放人 林奠驚犬承擔責任"},{"pid":"ffc6a3e7c34669e55a76d108bf6f5628f285f4d1","tid":1224742,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"Sor手機排版係柒啲"},{"pid":"7ce8adcd50b830aee19667dc41e0d1721ea5f44d","tid":1224742,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"以為係新歌"},{"pid":"f5bea89430f6f53f6039b8fe07055911b162bd8d","tid":1224742,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ce8adcd50b830aee19667dc41e0d1721ea5f44d","tid":1224742,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"以為係新歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"淨係識Hallelujah"},{"pid":"bad0791f38cca56f4323e459a764cf0c6fa69703","tid":1224742,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:46:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ec00555c0feaf3fdba7606a2c9a41380e6e37108","tid":1224742,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0896919bd743f3cd81621ae9499ba2391280775d","tid":1224742,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f55c442e38833a1cac28f2a3b28b35e55826fc3","tid":1224742,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited